**Normal tasks**: Unassigned `inbox` + idle implementation agent â†’ PATCH `{"assigned_agent_id":"UUID","status":"in_progress"}` + nudge. Review/QA/Architect validation tasks â†’ `"status":"review"`. frontendâ†’PF, backendâ†’PB, infra/deployâ†’DevOps.

### Step 3 â€” Route Review Tasks
**Only `review` tasks.** Do not nudge QA for inbox/in_progress tasks. Check approvals for each task.

